eft\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:windowtext\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:windowtext\">地点：盐城市第一人民医院南区门诊四楼会议室（盐城市人民南路<span>66</span>号）。五、本项目采用竞争性谈判方式。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:windowtext\">六、申请人有违反《盐城市市场廉政准则规定（试行）》中规定情形的，招标人将拒绝报名。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:windowtext\">七、招投标监督管理机构及投诉电话：盐城市第一人民医院监督审查室，联系电话<span>0515-66696810</span>。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;text-align:left;text-indent:24.0pt;\r\nline-height:26.0pt\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:宋体;\r\ncolor:windowtext\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;text-indent:20.95pt;line-height:17.55pt;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:\'Times New Roman\',\'serif\';color:black;margin-top:39.0pt;text-align:right;\r\ntext-indent:24.0pt;line-height:1.5;layout-grid-mode:char\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;color:windowtext\">盐城市第一人民医院</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align